{"tid":671952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬鷹九：談論中國人權 不用隨西方國家起舞","createTime":"2018-05-20T14:28:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T21:53:30.000Z","uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7bfe8db7d8bc0557df4097fcdf6473fc1e30d6fc","tid":671952,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T14:28:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://newtalk.tw/news/view/2012-12-19/32118\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2012-12-19%2F32118&d=jj8XANtLQWZIC%2B78AV9%2B8jQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=6294d894\" target=\"_blank\">http://newtalk.tw/news/view/2012-12-19/32118</a><br />\n馬英九昨（18）日表示，人權不分國界，他向來關切中國人權問題，這不是隨西方國家起舞，也不是趕時髦。蘇貞昌今天回應說，捍衛人權是普世的價值，也無東西方國家之分，要有真行動、真勇氣與真道德，是時時刻刻該做的，沒有所謂「時髦」、「不時髦」的問題。"},{"pid":"52c4d70bca13ade664b2a1ec71370015980ef02e","tid":671952,"uid":18127,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T21:50:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e80f816a8b989819ff5cd2a6e29c81a88d0dbf2","tid":671952,"uid":157138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52c4d70bca13ade664b2a1ec71370015980ef02e","tid":671952,"uid":18127,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T21:50:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T21:53:30.000Z","msg":"做到先算啦 中國不嬲用把口做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}